8-22T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母, 鑊鑊都凌晨最近咁撚好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早上最近wo"},{"pid":"963b41fc8376a509e2ea3aca2c487cc82de8566b","tid":369313,"uid":127269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"source??"},{"pid":"6a7e906ad2b315597d448d57996d14bc838ee61a","tid":369313,"uid":1424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>source??</blockquote><br />\n熱帶氣旋警告 16:45 更新<br />\n熱帶氣旋動向▼<br />\n最新風暴消息<br />\n<br />\n天鴿於過去數小時繼續增強，並穩定地靠近廣東沿岸。天文台將於短期內改發三號強風信號。<br />\n<br />\n按照現時預測路徑，天鴿會於明日（星期三）早上最接近香港，並可能在本港以南100公里範圍內掠過，對本港構成相當威脅。除非天鴿採取較遠離本港的路徑移動或減弱，否則天文台會在午夜前後考慮改發八號烈風或暴風信號。<br />\n<br />\n本港天氣正逐漸轉壞，有狂風大驟雨。由於明早正值漲潮，本港部分低窪地區可能出現嚴重水浸。市民應盡早做好所有防風防水浸措施。<br />\n<br />\n由於海面有大浪及湧浪，市民應遠離岸邊及停止所有水上活動。"},{"pid":"0daaeabc6aff580f40e31b4749aeaa3da08935df","tid":369313,"uid":124263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面班人係咪on9<br />\n個風聽日晏晝兩點先去到珠海喎</blockquote><br />\n證明大家為屌而屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a307dca7b86fab30119370795a01d6b34ab71c9","tid":369313,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面班人係咪on9<br />\n個風聽日晏晝兩點先去到珠海喎</blockquote><br />\n證明大家為屌而屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好明顯會打足全日"},{"pid":"d4d112f04be846454942b793977036d0689ed502","tid":369313,"uid":28800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:57:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc2a01565339f3fad1354fb4ce2f9957f87e4de7","tid":369313,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0